160
00:12:48,220 --> 00:12:50,900
I got up bleary-eyed in the middle of the night
to go to the bathroom,

161
00:12:51,140 --> 00:12:52,500
and I thought I was at home.

162
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:56,340
