555
00:31:48,940 --> 00:31:49,550
OK.

556
00:31:50,870 --> 00:31:51,790
It’s a deal.

557
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:53,060
Gu Yanluo!

558
00:31:54,150 --> 00:31:55,580
